verbose_text: Although the overlap in altered genes observed in the prostate cancer tumors was minimal when compared to the lung Pten d/d Smad4 d/d mouse model (data not shown), we found high expression of SPP1 and Elf3 in Pten d/d Smad4 d/d lung tumors (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), indicating that ELF3 might play the conserved role to drive cancer development and metastasis.
